SELECT info_type.info, movie_info.info_type_id FROM movie_info JOIN info_type ON info_type.id = movie_info.info_type_id WHERE movie_info.info <= 'Antithesis reveals the parallel lives of two strangers who become friends in an online suicide club chat room in the moments before their first in person meeting. M, a middle-aged man, loses his grip on reality after the death of his wife. She beckons him to join her from the grave, and unable to live without her, he makes a vow to follow her in death. A, on the other hand, is a teenage girl just returning from the hospital after a failed suicide attempt. In order to escape the incessant emotional abuse of her mother, A runs away from home to meet M. The two desperate souls come together in an abandoned theater, revealing the depths of their need for one another and the lengths to which humans will go to end the desperation of solitude.' AND movie_info.movie_id <= 2054168 AND info_type.id > 63 AND movie_info.id <= 4972898

select title.md5sum, comp_cast_type.id, complete_cast.movie_id, movie_keyword.id, min(complete_cast.status_id) from comp_cast_type JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.status_id = comp_cast_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = complete_cast.movie_id JOIN movie_keyword ON movie_keyword.movie_id = title.id where comp_cast_type.id < 1 AND title.episode_nr < 54 group by title.md5sum, comp_cast_type.id, complete_cast.movie_id, movie_keyword.id having min(complete_cast.status_id) > 3 order by title.md5sum DESC

SELECT aka_title.id, movie_link.linked_movie_id, kind_type.kind, title.imdb_index FROM movie_link JOIN title ON title.id = movie_link.movie_id JOIN kind_type ON kind_type.id = title.kind_id JOIN aka_title ON aka_title.kind_id = kind_type.id WHERE title.episode_of_id > 838473 AND aka_title.note >= '(Canada: French title)' AND title.season_nr <> 3

select keyword.keyword, keyword.phonetic_code from movie_keyword JOIN keyword ON keyword.id = movie_keyword.keyword_id where movie_keyword.movie_id >= 1718187 AND keyword.phonetic_code <= 'P4352' AND keyword.phonetic_code >= 'C4265' AND movie_keyword.movie_id = 1882109 order by keyword.keyword DESC, keyword.phonetic_code DESC

SELECT person_info.info_type_id, title.id, aka_title.episode_nr, movie_info.info, kind_type.kind, info_type.id FROM person_info JOIN info_type ON info_type.id = person_info.info_type_id JOIN movie_info ON movie_info.info_type_id = info_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info.movie_id JOIN aka_title ON aka_title.movie_id = title.id JOIN kind_type ON kind_type.id = aka_title.kind_id WHERE aka_title.id = 180596 AND title.series_years <> '1996-????'

select link_type.link, title.imdb_index, movie_link.movie_id, avg(movie_link.id), max(title.kind_id) from link_type, movie_link, title where title.imdb_index <= 'I' AND movie_link.linked_movie_id > 1394139 AND title.production_year = 1947 group by link_type.link, movie_link.movie_id, title.imdb_index order by movie_link.movie_id DESC

SELECT title.id, movie_info_idx.info_type_id, comp_cast_type.kind, complete_cast.id, SUM(complete_cast.subject_id) FROM movie_info_idx JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info_idx.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id JOIN comp_cast_type ON comp_cast_type.id = complete_cast.status_id WHERE movie_info_idx.info < '2..11111.3' AND title.season_nr > 3 GROUP BY title.id, movie_info_idx.info_type_id, comp_cast_type.kind, complete_cast.id HAVING SUM(complete_cast.subject_id) > 1

select keyword.keyword, movie_keyword.id from movie_keyword JOIN keyword ON keyword.id = movie_keyword.keyword_id where movie_keyword.movie_id >= 2046473 AND movie_keyword.keyword_id = 7869 AND keyword.id >= 5165 AND movie_keyword.id = 1402415 order by keyword.keyword DESC, movie_keyword.id DESC

select title.title, complete_cast.subject_id, movie_info.movie_id, movie_info_idx.info_type_id, info_type.info from movie_info JOIN info_type ON info_type.id = movie_info.info_type_id JOIN movie_info_idx ON movie_info_idx.info_type_id = info_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info_idx.movie_id JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.movie_id = title.id where title.md5sum = '888ce491c23a67e2c0dfd2899776a39f' AND movie_info_idx.movie_id = 2010299 order by complete_cast.subject_id DESC

select keyword.phonetic_code, movie_keyword.movie_id, sum(movie_keyword.movie_id), max(movie_keyword.keyword_id) from keyword JOIN movie_keyword ON movie_keyword.keyword_id = keyword.id where movie_keyword.id = 525101 AND keyword.id = 104859 AND keyword.phonetic_code <= 'N6253' group by keyword.phonetic_code, movie_keyword.movie_id order by keyword.phonetic_code DESC, movie_keyword.movie_id ASC

select title.title, complete_cast.status_id, comp_cast_type.kind, movie_info.info, sum(title.kind_id) from comp_cast_type JOIN complete_cast ON complete_cast.status_id = comp_cast_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = complete_cast.movie_id JOIN movie_info ON movie_info.movie_id = title.id where movie_info.info_type_id >= 65 AND movie_info.movie_id <= 1039881 AND title.md5sum < 'bbb03311ac842f628147975d1b093de0' group by title.title, complete_cast.status_id, comp_cast_type.kind, movie_info.info

select keyword.id, movie_keyword.movie_id from keyword, movie_keyword where keyword.id > 43184 AND keyword.phonetic_code = 'P4352' AND movie_keyword.movie_id >= 2217549 AND movie_keyword.id > 735536 AND keyword.phonetic_code < 'P4352' order by movie_keyword.movie_id DESC, keyword.id DESC

select link_type.id, title.md5sum, title.id, movie_link.id from movie_info JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info.movie_id JOIN movie_link ON movie_link.movie_id = title.id JOIN link_type ON link_type.id = movie_link.link_type_id where title.imdb_index = 'II' AND movie_info.movie_id >= 2059545 AND title.production_year < 1970 order by movie_link.id ASC

SELECT title.series_years, kind_type.id, movie_info.info_type_id FROM movie_info JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info.movie_id JOIN kind_type ON kind_type.id = title.kind_id WHERE title.episode_nr >= 48 AND title.kind_id = 7 AND title.production_year < 1970 AND title.phonetic_code > 'U4352' AND movie_info.note = '(Chicago International Film Festival)'

SELECT cast_info.person_id, name.name_pcode_cf, role_type.id FROM role_type, cast_info, name WHERE role_type.role = 'actress' AND name.id = 3038459 AND name.name_pcode_cf < 'H6252' AND cast_info.movie_id = 2171184 ORDER BY name.name_pcode_cf DESC

SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS producing_company, MIN(lt.link) AS link_type, MIN(t.title) AS complete_western_sequel FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, company_name AS cn, company_type AS ct, keyword AS k, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, movie_link AS ml, title AS t WHERE cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'crew') AND cct2.kind = 'complete' AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') AND ct.kind = 'production companies' AND k.keyword = 'sequel' AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%' AND mc.note IS NULL AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Germany', 'Swedish', 'German') AND t.production_year = 1998 AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.keyword_id = k.id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND mc.company_id = cn.id AND mi.movie_id = t.id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id

select movie_keyword.movie_id, title.episode_nr, movie_keyword.id, link_type.link from movie_keyword JOIN title ON title.id = movie_keyword.movie_id JOIN movie_link ON movie_link.movie_id = title.id JOIN link_type ON link_type.id = movie_link.link_type_id where movie_keyword.movie_id < 1908764 AND link_type.link >= 'spin off from' AND title.title >= '(#1.5035)' order by movie_keyword.id ASC, movie_keyword.movie_id DESC, link_type.link DESC, title.episode_nr ASC

select company_name.name, title.episode_of_id, info_type.id, movie_companies.company_type_id, movie_info_idx.movie_id from info_type JOIN movie_info_idx ON movie_info_idx.info_type_id = info_type.id JOIN title ON title.id = movie_info_idx.movie_id JOIN movie_companies ON movie_companies.movie_id = title.id JOIN company_name ON company_name.id = movie_companies.company_id where company_name.id >= 225408 AND title.season_nr >= 3 order by company_name.name ASC
